There 4 different types of food: grapes, papaya, raspberry, watermelon
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, mouse, rabbit
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, game, oliveros, baccarat
 1. the person eating grapes is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 2. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is between the person eating watermelon and the person eating raspberry##2
 6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
 8. the owner of the rabbit is the game-smoker##1
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the lizard is the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | soy-milk   | coffee | almond-milk | fanta      |
| Food        | watermelon | grapes | raspberry   | papaya     |
| Pet         | lizard     | cat    | mouse       | rabbit     |
| Cigar   | cain    | baccarat  | oliveros       | game |

