 7. the owner of the mouse is between the person driving the airplane and the owner of the bird##2
 8. the fan of pop is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
